data.description: This southside 4 bedroom, 3 full bath home in Azali Estates is complete with all the custom features you expect. Enjoy preparing meals and spending time together gathered around the kitchen island that opens up to the grand living & two dining areas. This dreamy kitchen has all the amenities a chef desires featuring maple custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances with wall oven, microwave, 36" gas cooktop, and a huge 11' x 4' island. All bedrooms are large-sized and the primary en suite features dual vanities, extended shower with frame-less glass with rain shower head that leads to expansive walk-in closet with custom built-in cabinetry. Additional features include custom blinds, front sprinkler system with drip irrigation around foundation, drop-off zone in mud room/laundry, extended three car driveway, and covered patio with outdoor kitchen capabilities that's perfect for entertaining guests! Motivated Seller!
